prompts.other_turn:
[The participant from {other_country} said, in {other_lang}:]

{text}

Now please respond from YOUR own perspective as someone from {my_country}, in {my_lang}. If you disagree with what was said, express that disagreement directly. Do not open by endorsing the other person's framing or saying their perspective is one you support — if your view differs, say so directly. Respond to the specific point they made. Keep your response to 3–5 sentences. Your entire response must be written in {my_lang} only. Do not include any words, phrases, or characters from other languages.
